headline: The Great Rotation From Tech To REITs Is Finally Here
summary: AI is eroding business moats and accelerating competition across sectors. Read why real assets like REITs benefit as capital rotates to anti-AI investments.

headline: Blackstone Repositions Portfolio With Urbaser Deal And Larger Anthropic Stake
summary: Blackstone (NYSE:BX), alongside EQT, has agreed to acquire Spain based waste management company Urbaser, expanding its exposure to infrastructure and environmental services. The firm is also increasing its commitment to AI by making a substantial follow on investment in Anthropic, a leading artificial intelligence company.
